{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":6,"day":24}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"海疆巡诊","authors":["郑寒前崔合美"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"波里摇，浪里颠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风催潮送海天间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们海岛医疗队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追逐鸥出港湾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天湛蓝，海湛蓝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海远天连一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅上的红旗指何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目标：海防最前线！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说有云雾锁碧水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波漩浪转击船舷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看红霞铺满海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光大道在眼前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条路，通向渔村和哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向阵地和壕堑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡诊路是战斗的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵着咱在腔热血和情感。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里，杆杆船桅在招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里，扇扇窗口把咱盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱是毛主席派来的送药人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快去看望钢铁连队英雄帆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船迎红日向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的道路步步宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船尾，浪迹一行牵云影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船头，金辉万点艳阳天！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}